title: Episode 172: The Sweetheart (Feat. Justine Skye)
itunes:title: Episode 172: The Sweetheart (Feat. Justine Skye)
description:
Singer Justine Skye joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and the ladies try and build their perfect man. Justine opens up about why she cries during sex, the ladies give her homework for her sex-life, and much more. Enjoy!
